description:
The Fusion Warrior from Dragon Ball GT, Gogeta (SS4), now comes to DRAGON BALL FighterZ!

This content includes:
• Gogeta (SS4) as a new playable character
• 5 alternative colors for his outfit
• Gogeta (SS4) Lobby Avatar
• Gogeta (SS4) Z Stamp
name: DRAGON BALL FIGHTERZ - Gogeta (SS4)
